data.description: Welcome to beautiful, serene Acampo in the heart of wine country. This home gives you the privacy, space and ability to live off the land yet still be close to modern amenities. Almost 6 acres of fully fenced land with cross fencing and remote controlled entrance gate. Primary home features 5 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, 3,097 sq.ft. with remodeled kitchen and owned SOLAR. Separate guest casita with kitchen and two full bathrooms. Primary home has been lovingly updated with new LVP flooring, paint and wait until you see the kitchen! Large island with tons of storage, farmhouse sink looking out through bay window to yard, custom hood over gas range with double ovens and pot filler. Custom cabinets, subway tile, quartz counters, all open to dining area and custom bar with sink, double wine refrigerators and keg taps. 3 bedrooms downstairs including primary bed/bath with access to back yard. An additional 2 large rooms upstairs perfect for office, game room or more bedrooms. Spacious 1,100 sq.ft. guest casita gives even more options for this wonderful property. Animal barn, hay storage, additional storage barn, koi pond with bridge, fruit tree orchard, garden, covered RV parking, and seasonal pond at back of property. Railroad track is not functional. Come view, so much to love!
